        public static RequirementsParser newXMLRequirementsParser​(List<Source> extensionSchemaSources)
                                                   throws MalformedURLException,
                                                          org.jdom2.JDOMException,
                                                          SAXException
        Constructs a requirements parser with a list of extension schema that describe possible requirements definition extensions.
        Parameters:
        extensionSchemaSources - extension schema that describe requirements definition extensions
        Returns:
        the new requirements parser instance
        Throws:
        org.jdom2.JDOMException - if an error occurred while constructing the JDOM2 SAX parser
        MalformedURLException - if one of the schema sources was a malformed URL
        SAXException - if an error occurred while parsing the schema

      • newSchemaAssessment

        public static SchemaAssessment newSchemaAssessment​(String derivedRequirementId,
                                                   List<? extends Source> schemaSources)
        Constructs a new XML schema-based Assessment that can be used to validate assessed documents against a set of XML schema. The result of the SchemaAssessment is reported against a single provided derived requirement identifier.
        Parameters:
        derivedRequirementId - the identifier of the derived requirement to report TestResult instances against based on the schema validation results
        schemaSources - a collection of Source instances that point to schema resources
        Returns:
        the new schema assessment instance
